{
  "_comment": [
    "Custom Links — appended to / merged into the built-in Links menu.",
    "",
    "This file is managed via Admin > UI tab > Custom Menu Links,",
    "or you can edit it directly and restart the server.",
    "",
    "HOW MERGING WORKS",
    "─────────────────",
    "Each entry in 'groups' is matched against the built-in groups in",
    "frontend-pages.json by the 'group' name (case-sensitive).",
    "",
    "  • If the name MATCHES a built-in group, your files/subgroups are",
    "    injected INTO that group — they appear alongside the built-in links.",
    "",
    "  • If the name does NOT match any built-in group, a brand-new group",
    "    is appended AFTER all built-in groups in the menu.",
    "",
    "SUPPORTED FIELDS",
    "────────────────",
    "Group level:",
    "  group      (required) — display name; must match a built-in group name",
    "                          to inject into it, or be unique to create a new group.",
    "  depends_on (optional) — hide this group if the named feature is disabled.",
    "                          Known keys: cw_skimmer, noise_floor, digital_decodes,",
    "                                      rotator, ant_switch.",
    "                          Only meaningful on NEW groups (built-in group",
    "                          visibility is controlled by the built-in config).",
    "  files      (optional) — array of direct links shown in this group.",
    "  subgroups  (optional) — array of named sub-menus, each with their own files.",
    "",
    "File / link level:",
    "  path        (required) — relative path (e.g. 'mypage.html') or full URL",
    "                           (https://...). Relative paths are served from the",
    "                           UberSDR web root.",
    "  name        (required) — label shown in the menu.",
    "  description (optional) — tooltip text shown on hover.",
    "  depends_on  (optional) — hide this link if the named feature is disabled.",
    "",
    "Subgroup level:",
    "  name  (required) — display name. If it matches an existing built-in subgroup",
    "                     name, files are injected into that subgroup.",
    "  files (optional) — array of link entries (same fields as above).",
    "",
    "Remove the '_comment' key before using this file, or leave it — it is ignored",
    "by the server."
  ],
  "groups": [
    {
      "_comment": "Example 1: inject a link INTO an existing built-in group.",
      "group": "Propagation Conditions",
      "files": [
        {
          "path": "https://prop.example.com/",
          "name": "My Propagation Tool",
          "description": "Custom propagation analysis tool for this station."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "_comment": "Example 2: inject a new subgroup into an existing built-in group.",
      "group": "Clients",
      "subgroups": [
        {
          "name": "My Tools",
          "files": [
            {
              "path": "https://mytool.example.com/",
              "name": "My Custom Tool",
              "description": "A custom tool specific to this station."
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "_comment": "Example 3: inject a link into an existing built-in subgroup by matching its name.",
      "group": "Clients",
      "subgroups": [
        {
          "name": "Desktop Client",
          "files": [
            {
              "path": "https://example.com/my-client.exe",
              "name": "My Custom Client",
              "description": "A custom desktop client build."
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "_comment": "Example 4: create a brand-new group (name does not match any built-in group).",
      "group": "My Station",
      "files": [
        {
          "path": "https://www.qrz.com/db/M0XYZ",
          "name": "QRZ Page",
          "description": "My QRZ.com operator page."
        },
        {
          "path": "https://www.hamlog.example.com/",
          "name": "Log Book",
          "description": "Online log book for this station."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "_comment": "Example 5: new group with a depends_on — only shown when CW Skimmer is enabled.",
      "group": "Local Resources",
      "depends_on": "cw_skimmer",
      "files": [
        {
          "path": "https://cluster.example.com/",
          "name": "Local DX Cluster",
          "description": "Regional DX cluster for this station."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "_comment": "Example 6: new group with subgroups.",
      "group": "Downloads",
      "subgroups": [
        {
          "name": "Software",
          "files": [
            {
              "path": "https://example.com/software.zip",
              "name": "My Software",
              "description": "Custom software download."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "name": "Documentation",
          "files": [
            {
              "path": "https://docs.example.com/",
              "name": "Station Docs",
              "description": "Documentation for this station's setup."
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
}
